strategies.name: Aggressive Maximizer
strategies.strategy: Demand the largest possible share. Use threats and aggressive tactics. Form coalitions only when absolutely necessary to avoid elimination.

strategies.name: Diplomatic Builder
strategies.strategy: Build long-term trust through consistently fair offers. Prioritize mutual benefit and stable coalitions. Avoid betrayals.

strategies.name: Strategic Opportunist
strategies.strategy: Adapt rapidly to changing situations. Form and break alliances based on immediate advantage. Keep all options open.

strategies.name: Mathematical Analyzer
strategies.strategy: Make all decisions based on expected value calculations. Minimize risk through probability analysis. Avoid emotional decisions.

strategies.name: Social Manipulator
strategies.strategy: Use psychological tactics to influence others. Make strategic promises and betrayals. Create chaos to exploit confusion.

strategies.strategy: Analyze opponent negotiation patterns, proposal behaviors, and voting tendencies to identify their strategies. Adapt your approach to optimally counter each opponent type in real-time.
